These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, artichoke, pumpkin, lettuce
1. the person eating cabbage is on the far left##1
2. the person eating artichoke is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
3. the person eating artichoke is on the left or right of the person eating pumpkin##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | cabbage | artichoke | pumpkin | lettuce |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, soy-milk, juice
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | sprite | cola | juice | soy-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, gardening, woodworking, puzzles
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | dancing | woodworking | gardening | puzzles |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, documentary, western, satire
1. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | martial-arts | satire | western |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
