2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Sport   | volleyball | ice-hockey | snowboarding | cycling |

