2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
3. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2    |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | goldfish | frog | guinea-pig | cat |

