.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, disco, salsa, metal
1. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of metal##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of disco##1
3. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
4. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | disco | country | metal |

 